  npcSprite: {fileID: 7310064867776009774, guid: 54f4007506920af44bcc6b7374d1e5c3, type: 3}
  options:
  - optionText: I'm fully aware of what we'd need to do to test the softness! It
      wouldn't be the first time we had a sleepover!
